references: Related: Ord 81186, CF 218621. Amends: Ord 45382. Supersedes: Ord 81275.
summary: An ordinance zoning and establishing Use, Area and Height Districts on portions of Section 29 and 32, Township 26 North, Range 4 E., W. M., annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 81186 on August 20, 1952, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, to embrace such area.
